            References: Erotrokitou, Chrystel. 2012. “Sovereignty Over Airspace: International Law, Current Challenges and Future Developments for Global Aviation”. Student Pulse. Accessed April 21, 2014. Available in: http://www.studentpulse.com/articles/645/sovereignty-over-airspace-international-law-current-challenges-and-future-developments-for-global-aviation.
